<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="A" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="April" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">April,</orth> the fourth month: <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.281" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 281</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 4.2.120" default="NO" valid="yes">John IV, 2, 120</bibl>. It is the month of spring and flowers: <bibl n="shak. son 3.10" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 3, 10</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 4.21.7" default="NO" valid="yes">21, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 4.98.2" default="NO" valid="yes">98, 2</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 4.104.7" default="NO" valid="yes">104, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. luc 395" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 395</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.2.69" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 2, 69</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.93" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 9, 93</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ayl 4.1.147" default="NO" valid="yes">As IV, 1, 147</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.2.27" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 2, 27</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tim 4.3.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. IV, 3, 41</bibl>; though a month of inconstant weather, <bibl n="shak. tgv 1.3.85" default="NO" valid="yes">Gentl. I, 3, 85</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lc 102" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 102</bibl>; and of much rain: <bibl n="shak. tmp 4.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. IV, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 1.2.189" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 2, 189</bibl> (<emph>he will weep you, an 'twere a man born in April</emph>). <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.18" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. III, 1, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.2.43" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 2, 43</bibl> <emph>(the A. 's in her eyes).</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>